The paper discusses the fundamental limits and optimal signalling strategies of LPD communication, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). LPD communication is also relevant to wireless networks (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY) as it addresses privacy and security issues. Additionally, the paper mentions the challenges in designing practical LPD communication systems, which may involve multimedia communication (cs.MM).
